These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, orchid
City: hamburg, marseilles
2 different games are played: canasta, go
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, swisher
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, aquamarine
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, thai
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
2. the person who growsorchid is not to the right of the bolivar-smoker##8
3. the person playing go is not the person who likes yellow##6
4. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the swisher-smoker##5
5. the swisher-smoker is not to the left of the person driving the roller##8
6. the thai is not the person driving the roller##6
7. the person traveling to hamburg is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Flower      | orchid   | tulip      |
| City          | marseilles | hamburg   |
| Game         | go    | canasta |
| Cigar           | bolivar     | swisher    |
| Color   | aquamarine    | yellow       |
| Nationality   | italian    | thai        |
| Transport     | roller     | tram        |

